war it cant be done from the air or with hightech warfare alone 
i dont think you can win it by bombing iraq said jack n 
meritt a retired fourstar army general who was the us 
representative to natos military committee weve been trying 
that since world war ii and there has been no case in history where 
youve been able to defeat a force on the ground from the air 
fighting the iraqis in kuwait would be difficult fighting 
