12party unity assembly politcal coalition 
mrs pascaltrouillot a former supreme court judge was 
appointed by the unity assembly on march 13 after the fall of lt 
gen prosper avril who had taken power in september 1988 during a 
soldiers rebellion that toppled the previous government 
mrs pascaltrouillot was to govern jointly with a council of 
