346 to use the same facsimile service to transmit a page to the 
middle east he added that atampt had installed 25 facsimile machines 
at an undisclosed location in the middle east to handle the 
messages 
a facsimile or fax machine takes a printed page and 
translates it into electronic signals that are sent through the 
phone network and reprinted by a distant facsimile machine 
