because it is so dry 
the drought has left the vegetation just crackling dry he 
said 
more than 1300 firefighters are battling the fire their task 
made all the more difficult by the steep and difficult terrain in 
the canyon the blaze was 40 percent contained this morning 
the firefighters are up against the very worst in this fire 
kaunert said adding that the area is so dry that the fire is 
spreading rapidly even without winds 
