plant virtually inaccessible he said 
the mystery unraveled thursday when a sister of one of rickys 
playmates overheard a conversation in which the boy said ricky had 
fallen she told her mother who notified police 
the boys entered the silo which had a locked door and climbed 
15 flights of stairs to get to the top guest said 
the area was fenced but these are little boys they had no 
problem getting over the fence she said its still unclear 
how they got into the building 
guest said the area had been abandoned for more than a decade 
she said she knew of no other reports or complaints of children 
entering the area 
on the afternoon of april 26 ricky stopped at home and asked 
his father what time he should be home for dinner it was the last 
time his family saw the fifthgrader 
well everybody can stop looking said the boys father 
steve rodriguez i thought he was dead the night he disappeared 
it just didnt fit his pattern but i was hoping 
