a 459 million bus tunnel opens saturday after 
four years of rippedup streets and traffic nightmares offering to 
zip commuters through congested downtown in about onethird the 
time it takes on the surface 
the twolane tunnel is expected to reduce downtown bus traffic 
25 percent by next fall and 40 percent by the end of the decade 
