finances in his absence 
murphy who was seeking the democratic nomination for governor 
unveiled her budget plans sept 7 but she could not escape charges 
that her tactics were designed to bolster her failing campaign 
murphy dropped out of the governors race monday she said se 
would continue to fight for her plans contained in executive 
orders she signed last week 
dukakis whose popularity has plummeted along with his states 
economy decided not to run for reelection this year 
economic woes were on his mind when he returned from europe i 
will take advice from anybody and everybody who can constructively 
participate in this that includes the lieutenant governor he 
said at a news conference at logan international airport 
murphy said her plans would save the state about 150 million 
annually she called for slashing about 1000 jobs from the state 
