negotiations said jerry gorski financial secretary of uaw local 
634 in buffalo ny whatever theyve got theyre keeping it 
under their hats 
i imagine theyll probably have an extension 
any strike called by the uaw wouldnt have any significant 
effects until monday most gm plants are scheduled to close for the 
weekend 
