monday in dearborn a suburb of detroit for local presidents and 
bargaining committee heads that announcement prompted speculation 
that negotiators were closer to a settlement than a strike 
another union official said the meeting could be used to brief 
union leaders on a strike but it more likely would be used to 
discuss a tentative settlement 
uaw locals nationwide put the finishing touches on strike plans 
thursday 
mike obrien president of uaw local 95 at gms janesville 
wis truck and bus plant said his members were prepared for a 
strike picket line assignments have been made and signs will be 
ready by the deadline 
