of the canadian auto workers and fords canadian subsidiary over a 
contract covering about 12800 workers like the uawgm contract 
the cawford agreement expires at midnight 
the rhetoric in the toronto talks has been much higher than in 
the us negotiations caw president bob white said the two sides 
remain far apart 
